replies.body:
Mohammad,

The Grizzly Bear component is still in WIP and we don't have full support for it yet.  I was hoping to show it some love and work on it more in the next couple of months.  In the meantime, Mostapha probably has the most up-to-date-knowledge on the current component.

I'll post here if I get the chance to work on it at any point.

-Chris

Thank you very much Chris for your reply and letting me know fast!

Best.

-M
